                " at sample position. Neutron flux was determined by",
                " the activity of gold foils."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Two different types of commercially available metallic",
                "Fe powder from Merc (Fe-M) and Alfa Aesar (Fe-A) with",
                "natural abundances ( 5.8% Fe-54) for two irradiations.",
                "Each was sandwiched between two gold foils of the same",
                "diameter. Placed in close geometry to the Li target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
